metadata.name: I Would Like to Hide My Evil in a Magic Mushroom
metadata.description:
Full Title:
I Would Like to Hide My Evil in a Magic Mushroom Forest

We all live in a state of duality. Yin Yang powers are all around and inside of us.  We have powerful thoughts inside of us, some remain hidden from view, perhaps in a secret walled garden in our minds? Or maybe .... a Magic Mushroom Forest?

Hand drawn Mushroom Forest and real time, hand driven AI GAN + music - KUSH

1536x1536 px
